===========================================================
AI AGENT RULES
===========================================================

Before writing code, always ask yourself:

1. Does this already exist somewhere else in the project?

2. Can this be reused instead of rewritten?

3. Am I introducing duplicate logic?

4. Does this implementation respect the current architecture?

5. Will another engineer understand this code in six months?

If the answer to any of these is NO, redesign before coding.

Never optimize for writing more code.

Optimize for writing better software.